{"tid":670026,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明明是「華南地區」，立場新聞的編輯卻情花毒上腦，寫成是「中國南部」","createTime":"2018-05-19T04:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T07:06:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"441757b4dc68b03918b1eb9cc56df8dfdd5faebb","tid":670026,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/19/120444_bb3fc14d75c051185a7529c514e8a0b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F19%2F120444_bb3fc14d75c051185a7529c514e8a0b8.png&h=2964b972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明是「華南地區」，立場新聞的編輯卻情花毒上腦，寫成是「中國南部」，甚至荒謬到連漢人仍在黃河流域，就把華南的古人類寫成是「中國人大遷徙」，再次說明民族主義洗腦，有幾可怕。<br />\n<br />\n更可笑的，係圖中大大隻「中國」，真係「自古以來」都係「中國」呀？西方的地理名詞，譯成漢文就變晒做民族主義的國家觀念，成件事真係好荒謬－－果班人講南亞語系與南島語系，係菲律賓人泰國人越南人緬甸人與印尼人的祖先來的，幾時交還華南畀佢地呀？"},{"pid":"c41bfb561b40c64202fb2141db7e28e378bc6eee","tid":670026,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10155272142921121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffokguy%2Fposts%2F10155272142921121&d=QhqAE%2BowGebsppo1Z3Gpx5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=b650b81b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10155272142921121</a>"},{"pid":"7352a38ce8e3ec01e84b6310c1702974ca1f38ae","tid":670026,"uid":54733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"長江以南班講壯侗語系嘅古民族慘被老屈成中國人"},{"pid":"191ea05d5e219169b65c3c8705e50b30fc3c25d8","tid":670026,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:18:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"969d2326c3541e78292b3e0a4b3ad6f5a3adeaf7","tid":670026,"uid":22566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:23:01.000Z","msg":"一早整個新民族出來咪冇咁麻煩囉<br />\n三日唔埋就俾人抽秤 又悶又煩"},{"pid